 ğŸ—‚ï¸ 3. Bucket Versioning

 âœ… Definition

Bucket Versioning ek feature hai jisme:

> Ek hi file ke multiple versions bucket me store hote hain.

---

 ğŸ” What Versioning Does?

 File delete hone par recover kar sakte ho
 File overwrite hone par old version safe rehta hai

---

 ğŸªœ How to Enable Bucket Versioning

1. S3 bucket open karo
2. Go to Properties
3. Bucket Versioning â†’ Enable
4. Save changes

---

 âš ï¸ 4. VERY IMPORTANT CONCEPT

 â“ â€œData update replace nahi hotaâ€ â€“ iska kya matlab hai?

 âœ… Simple Explanation

Jab Bucket Versioning ENABLED hoti hai:

ğŸ‘‰ Agar tum:

 Same file naam se naya data upload karte ho

Toh:

 Old file replace nahi hoti
 New file ek naya version ban jati hai

---

 ğŸ§  Example (Easy to Understand)

ğŸ“„ File: `report.pdf`

 Version 1 â†’ Old report
 Version 2 â†’ Updated report

ğŸ‘‰ Dono versions bucket me rehte hain
ğŸ‘‰ Latest version default dikhta hai

---

 âŒ Without Versioning

 Old file delete ho jaati
 Recover possible nahi

---

 âœ… With Versioning

 Old data safe
 Recovery possible

---

 ğŸ’¡ Why This is Important?

 Accidentally delete hone se bachav
 Data loss protection
 Audit & backup purpose

---

 ğŸ”„ Lifecycle + Versioning Together

Lifecycle rules:

 Old versions ko Glacier me move kar sakti hain
 Ya automatically delete kar sakti hain

ğŸ‘‰ Isse cost bhi bachta hai.

